  %h2 RHoK Global Hackathon - 1st & 2nd of June

  %p The next RHoK is approaching fast. You can sign up to the event via Eventbrite

  %p  See our Press Release here. Our post-event Press Release is here.

  %p  RHoK Melbourne will be located at Swinburne University Hawthorn, in the TD building.

    
  %h3  Saturday June 1st
  %ul
    %li 9.00 – 9.30 Get set up, and ready for 2 great days
    %li 9.30 – 9.45 Welcome and administrivia
    %li 9.45 - 10.30 Choosing problem areas to work on, and teams to work with
    %li 11.00 - 19.00 start your hacking
    %li 19.00 – 20.00 Dinner (on us)
    %li 20.00 – 02.00 more time to design and develop
    
  %p We'll have light snacks, fruit, drinks and the like on hand to keep your blood sugar levels up. There are many great local cafes, restaurants and stores around to grab a more substantial lunch

  %p You can work as late as 2.00am, or head home a little earlier to catch up on some sleep

  %h3  Sunday June 2nd
  %ul
    %li 8.00 – 13.00 Coding continues
    %li 14.00 Time to down tools
    %li 14.30 – 15.30 All projects get 10 minutes to present their work to all (and the judges)
    %li 15.30 – 16.00 Judges deliberate
    %li 16.00 – 16.30 Awards and prizes
    %li 16.30 onwards - come share a drink nearby at the Hotel Hotham to unwind
